test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[-72], [-72], [-72]]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: [-72]
  Full diff:
  - [[-72], [-72], [-72]]
  + []
test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[-72]]
  Right contains one more item: [-72]
  Full diff:
  - [[-72]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -10368 == -72
 +  where -10368 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -2, -3, -4, -6, -8, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
